		<div class="comment-metadata">
			<p class="comment-permalink"><a href="https://terrytao.wordpress.com/2015/09/29/275a-notes-0-foundations-of-probability-theory/#comment-459928" title="Permalink to this comment">1 October, 2015 at 12:38 pm</a></p>
