	<div class="comment even thread-even depth-1 vcard parent highlander-comment" id="comment-460003">
		<div class="comment-metadata">
			<p class="comment-permalink"><a href="https://terrytao.wordpress.com/2015/09/29/275a-notes-0-foundations-of-probability-theory/#comment-460003" title="Permalink to this comment">2 October, 2015 at 12:31 pm</a></p>
			<p class="comment-author"><strong class="fn">Travis</strong></p>
					</div>

		<div class="comment-content">
			<img alt="" src="https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/9f1629fd5354946c709e4ac371c20d4c?s=32&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=PG" class="avatar avatar-32 grav-hashed grav-hijack" height="32" width="32" id="grav-9f1629fd5354946c709e4ac371c20d4c-0">			<p>In Definition #1, the discrete sample space <img src="https://s0.wp.com/latex.php?latex=%5COmega&amp;bg=ffffff&amp;fg=545454&amp;s=0" alt="\Omega" title="\Omega" class="latex"> is defined in terms of itself using <img src="https://s0.wp.com/latex.php?latex=%5COmega&amp;bg=ffffff&amp;fg=545454&amp;s=0" alt="\Omega" title="\Omega" class="latex"> again.  Is this circular definition intentional?  Why not use a different designation for the discrete sample space?</p>
<div class="pd-rating" id="pd_rating_holder_132742_comm_460003" style="display: inline-block;"><div class="rating-icons" id="pd_rate_132742_comm_460003" style="float:left;"><div class="rating-nero-icon" onmouseout="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003.rebuild();" onclick="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003.rate(1);" onmouseover="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003.hover(1);" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003_nero_1" style="background-size: 32px 32px !important; cursor: pointer; width: 16px; height: 16px;  line-height: 16px; background: url(https://polldaddy.com/images/ratings/nero-hand-sml.png) bottom left; float: left; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div><div class="rating-nero-value" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003_msg_1" style="text-align: center; font:normal normal /16px ; color: #; float:left; padding: 0px 4px;">0</div><div class="rating-nero-icon" onmouseout="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003.rebuild();" onclick="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003.rate(2);" onmouseover="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003.hover(2);" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003_nero_2" style="background-size: 32px 32px !important; cursor: pointer; width: 16px; height: 16px;  line-height: 16px; background: url(https://polldaddy.com/images/ratings/nero-hand-sml.png) bottom right; float: left; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div><div class="rating-nero-value" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003_msg_2" style="text-align: center; font:normal normal /16px ; color: #; float:left; padding: 0px 4px;">0</div></div><span style="float:left;">&nbsp;</span><div id="rating_info_132742_comm_460003" style="display:block;float:left;background:url(https://polldaddy.com/images/ratings/info.png) no-repeat 3px 2px;width:16px;height:16px;cursor:pointer; null " onclick="javascript:PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003.togglePopup();return false;"><span style="display:none;">i</span></div><div class="pd_popup_holder" id="pd_popup_holder_132742_comm_460003">&nbsp;</div><div class="rating-msg" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_460003_msg" style="float:left; padding-left: 5px;