		<div class="comment-content">
			<img alt="" src="https://i1.wp.com/lh3.googleusercontent.com/-XdUIqdMkCWA/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAAA/4252rscbv5M/photo.jpg?resize=32%2C32&amp;ssl=1" class="avatar avatar-32" height="32" width="32">			<p>Dear Professor Tao, have you thought about videotaping your classes so that students can benefit from your lectures in a better way, especially given that real analysis and probability theory  have a large audience other than PhD students in Math, e.g., engineering, physics, economics, and finance?</p>
