		<div class="comment-content">
			<img alt="" src="https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/d1092312fa69898c042b4042ece9ec8b?s=32&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=PG" class="avatar avatar-32 grav-hashed grav-hijack" height="32" width="32" id="grav-d1092312fa69898c042b4042ece9ec8b-1">			<p>Example 9 : for “Becaue” read “Because” ;<br>
Exercise 15 : for “{\sigma-}algebra” read ” {\sigma}-algebra” ;<br>
Remark 25 foll. : delete “if one is ” ; for “if one has” read “when” .</p>
