	<div class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 vcard highlander-comment" id="comment-474350">
		<div class="comment-metadata">
			<p class="comment-permalink"><a href="https://terrytao.wordpress.com/2015/09/29/275a-notes-0-foundations-of-probability-theory/#comment-474350" title="Permalink to this comment">14 November, 2016 at 6:57 am</a></p>
			<p class="comment-author"><strong class="fn">Anonymous</strong></p>
					</div>

		<div class="comment-content">
			<img alt="" src="https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=32&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=PG" class="avatar avatar-32 grav-hashed grav-hijack" height="32" width="32" id="grav-false-16">			<p>Are “conjunction” and “disjunction” actually “set” operations and it is just because we want to distinguish explicitly an event and its model in a sample space <img src="https://s0.wp.com/latex.php?latex=%5COmega&amp;bg=ffffff&amp;fg=545454&amp;s=0" alt="\Omega" title="\Omega" class="latex"> that we deliberately use different terminologies than those in set theory?</p>
<div class="pd-rating" id="pd_rating_holder_132742_comm_474350" style="display: inline-block;"><div class="rating-icons" id="pd_rate_132742_comm_474350" style="float:left;"><div class="rating-nero-icon" onmouseout="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350.rebuild();" onclick="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350.rate(1);" onmouseover="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350.hover(1);" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350_nero_1" style="background-size: 32px 32px !important; cursor: pointer; width: 16px; height: 16px;  line-height: 16px; background: url(https://polldaddy.com/images/ratings/nero-hand-sml.png) bottom left; float: left; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div><div class="rating-nero-value" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350_msg_1" style="text-align: center; font:normal normal /16px ; color: #; float:left; padding: 0px 4px;">0</div><div class="rating-nero-icon" onmouseout="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350.rebuild();" onclick="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350.rate(2);" onmouseover="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350.hover(2);" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350_nero_2" style="background-size: 32px 32px !important; cursor: pointer; width: 16px; height: 16px;  line-height: 16px; background: url(https://polldaddy.com/images/ratings/nero-hand-sml.png) bottom right; float: left; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; margin: 0px;">&nbsp;</div><div class="rating-nero-value" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350_msg_2" style="text-align: center; font:normal normal /16px ; color: #; float:left; padding: 0px 4px;">0</div></div><span style="float:left;">&nbsp;</span><div id="rating_info_132742_comm_474350" style="display:block;float:left;background:url(https://polldaddy.com/images/ratings/info.png) no-repeat 3px 2px;width:16px;height:16px;cursor:pointer; null " onclick="javascript:PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350.togglePopup();return false;"><span style="display:none;">i</span></div><div class="pd_popup_holder" id="pd_popup_holder_132742_comm_474350">&nbsp;</div><div class="rating-msg" id="PDRTJS_132742_comm_474350_msg" style="float:left; padding-left: 5px;